name: ingenuity
author: The Temporal Reality Team
description:
Where's all the mods I am used to? 
 Maybe you will need to use some ingenuity to do what you are so used to doing!
 This pack contains a variety of mods which are not commonplace in mod packs, while keeping some 'fan favourites'
